data.title: Live My Life (song)
authors: Contributors to Lana Del Rey Wiki
data.meta_description: "Live My Life" is a song by Australian duo Nicholas Potts and Jay Lyon, known as Tamarama, from their debut self-titled album, released June 1, 2010. Lana Del Rey - then performing as Lizzy Grant - has uncredited backing vocals on the song. On May 3, 2010, David Kahne contacted Del Rey on...
